Google Play Services
Firebase Analytics
DroidPass use Firebase Analytics to monitor Crash log data from your app. For example, the number of times your app has crashed, stack traces, or other information directly related to a crash.
Security
DroidPass Password Manager hosts its infrastructure with Firebase with 24x7 monitoring, surveillance and support to prevent unauthorised access and data security and all your data store in it with strong 256 encryption alogorithm.
Data Deletion
The developer provides a way for you to request that your data be deleted.User can easily delete data from their app setting.
Your Master Pin
You hereby understand that upon using the application, you will be required to create a "Master Pin." 
The Master Pin will be used by you and only you. You are responsible for maintaining the security of your 
Master Pin  and DroidPass records entered using the application. DroidPass has no knowledge of 
your Master Pin and will not ask or be permitted to ask for your Master Pin. DroidPass, will not under 
any circumstances, have access to your Master Password or the records stored in DroidPass. You agree to 
not issue your Master Pin to any third parties and shall not, under any circumstances, issue your Master Pin 
to any customer support representative of DroidPass in the event you contact DroidPass for application
 assistance. Generally, you will agree to not share your Master Pin with any employee, agent, officer or 
director of DroidPass. DroidPass shall not be responsible for the actions of any individuals who misuse or 
misappropriate your DroidPass information or other any of your assets using your Master Pin or the 
information stored in DroidPass. Please remember your Master Pin. If you lose or forget your Master Pin, 
DroidPass will not be able to assist you in gaining access to your records since DroidPass does not have 
access to or knowledge of your Master Pin. Again, it is imperative to not forget your Master Pin since this is 
required to gain access to your records stored in DroidPass.
